    <stitle>13 SPEED AND 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-713/18 SERIES - INSTALL - ROADRANGER VALVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>ROADRANGER VALVE</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>To position the Roadranger valve, the range lever must be to the front or the splitter button to
                    the left when facing forward.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Make sure the nut, valve cover, air lines, sheathing, and O-rings are in position on the
                lever shaft.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If previously removed, replace the air fittings (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r4">Figure 274</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007r4" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007r4" filename="../figg13/G13007R4.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 274. Place Roadranger Valve on Lever Shaft</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the Roadranger valve on the lever shaft and rotate into position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r4">Figure 274</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">From the Roadranger valve bottom, tighten the jam nut (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r4">Figure 274</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect the air lines to the air fittings (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r5">Figure 275</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007r5" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007r5" filename="../figg13/G13007R5.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 275. Connect Air Lines to Air Fittings</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Slide the cover into position on the Roadranger valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r6">Figure 276</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007r6" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007r6" filename="../figg13/G13007R6.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 276. Slide Cover into Position on Roadranger Valve</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the Roadranger valve cover two (2) mounting screws (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r6">Figure 276</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
